Cell[TextData[{
 "Apparently, it looks different from the desired state ",
 StyleBox["raw", "Input"],
 " shown above. However, this is because of a physically irrelevant global \
phase. Indeed, the fidelity between the two states are unity:"
}], "ExampleText",
